<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="Aink214-kilavi"> talaimakaṉ oruvaḻittaṇappa leṉṟu kūṟiyavataṉai yavaṉ ciṟaippuṟattāṉākat talaimakaṭku+ tōḻi colliyatu.  </p>
      <p xml:lang="en"> What the confidante told the heroine while the hero was behind the hedge about what he had said: “I will be temporarily absent.”  </p>
      </div>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink214">
<l>cāraṟ palaviṉ koḻuntuṇar naṟumpaḻa</l>
<l>miruṅkal viṭaraḷai vīḻnteṉa veṟpiṟ</l>
<l>peruntē ṉiṟāal kīṟu nāṭaṉ</l>
<l>pēramar maḻaikkaṇ kaliḻattaṉ</l>
<l>cīruṭai naṉṉāṭṭuc cellu maṉṉāy</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">

<l>The man from the land </l>
<l rend="indent space"> where [clusters of jackfruit] split the huge honeycombs on the mountain</l>
<l rend="indent">because [those] fragrant fruits in large clusters </l>
<l rend="indent">from the jackfruit trees along the mountain slope fell </l>
<l rend="indent">into a cleft-hole, </l>
<l rend="space">will go to his good land which possesses excellence, </l>
<l>for [your] large, desirous, teary eyes to weep, mother!  </l>

      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
